	  <para>Here are some guidelines on how to use a RICE table:</para>
	  <list list-type="enumerated">
	    <item>
	      <para>Fill in the balanced chemical equation: <latex>\textcolor{blue}{\text{aA}} + \textcolor{blue}{\text{bB}} \rightleftharpoons \textcolor{red}{\text{cC}} + \textcolor{red}{\text{dD}}</latex></para>
		  <table>
		    <tgroup cols="5">
		      <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" style:latex-alignment="p{0.31\textwidth}"/>
