	      <workstep>
		<title>Determine which compounds are the reactants and which are the products</title>
		<para>The concentration of reactants decreases from the start of the reaction to equilibrium. Therefore <emphasis effect="italics">A</emphasis> and <emphasis effect="italics">B</emphasis> are reactants.</para>
		<para>The concentration of products increases from the start of the reaction to equilibrium. Therefore <emphasis effect="italics">C</emphasis> is a product.</para>
