		<para>When enough gas has collected in the syringe, the delivery tube is clamped so that no gas can escape. The brown <chem_compound>NO_{2}</chem_compound> gas collected reaches an equilibrium with colourless <chem_compound>N_{2}O_{4}</chem_compound> gas as represented by the following equation:</para>
