	      <para>Once this equilibrium has been established, there are <unit_number><number>0.01</number><unit>moles</unit></unit_number> of <chem_compound>NO_{2}</chem_compound> gas and <unit_number><number>0.03</number><unit>moles</unit></unit_number> of <chem_compound>N_{2}O_{4}</chem_compound> gas present in the syringe.</para>
