	      </problem>
	      <solution>
		<para><chem_compound>K_{c}</chem_compound> is the equilibrium constant, therefore it cannot be calculated except when the reaction is in equilibrium. During the first <unit_number><number>5</number><unit>minutes</unit></unit_number> the reaction is not in equilibrium.</para>
