		<para><unit_number><number>1</number><unit>cm<sup>3</sup></unit></unit_number> of distilled water</para>
	      </problem>
	      <solution>
		<para>The concentration of reactant (water) is increased, therefore the equilibrium will shift to the right and so the colour will <correct>change to pink</correct>.</para>
	      </solution>
