	      <problem>
		<para>A few crystals of sodium chloride</para>
	      </problem>
	      <solution>
		<para>The concentration of product (<chem_compound>Cl^{-}</chem_compound>) is increased, therefore the equilibrium will shift to the left and the colour <correct>will change to blue</correct>.</para>
